{
  "stem": "19211.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But still this is, I think, the most important thing for a Jew, in my opinion.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't tell you anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it's pure luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just pure luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I told you about the German coming out to my hiding place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know he wasn't stupid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He knew I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had to know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is no way that he would be that-- that stupid, because the hole is there, and just go under the wall.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were there in the other section, if you can understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was pure luck, I think, that he hollered down there to the other guys, there's nobody here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We can go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could've just said, come and look for people here, hiding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew-- the hiding place was given out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody gave him the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew exactly where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there for about-- I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want to say how long-- quite a few months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, we all-- dad used to go out to get food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They saw him, at night, go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They must have seen him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they know that there were Jews there, the two families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they gave them exactly the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew where we were and everything, exactly, where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because where we were hiding, that hole in the kitchen, they had one-room apartment there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With a kitchen floor-- there was a kitchen and dining room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put a-- a piece of furniture over top of it so you couldn't-- it's masking, you couldn't see the hole.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the German came, I remember he tried to get the piece of furniture right off.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
